{"tid":1707212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］覺得運動去到今日好需要真罷工既入！","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:56:59.000Z","uid":30138,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38477b4323c844c06849c558132519070080d709","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽既說話你想唔想聽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實就係，無論85 92 93定今日1111，果D都唔係真三罷，因為我地冇有系統地及長期地癱瘓到經濟，我地充其量都只係叫約左個日子出來打大交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工唔係講玩，冇灰色地帶，冇得兄弟爬山！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n因為當多一個人返工，罷工手足造成既經濟影響就越少<br />\n<br />\n因為當多一個人返工，罷工手足就越易比人針對同清算<br />\n<br />\n因為當多一個人返工，罷工手足就越覺得無力同易被取代<br />\n<br />\n無論係打狗定罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">義士都唔係condom</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">義士都唔係condom</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">義士都唔係condom</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果我地希望搞一場真罷工<br />\n<br />\n咁我地需要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）入會入會入會</span></span><br />\n相信大家都見到網上不斷有人講要罷工，已經有手足搞咗個🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴頻道 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=0d3a7b4d\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a>有睇Gay巴post就一定會見到<br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係話罷就罷到，第一步就係組工會，籌組工會係齊上齊落嘅指標。罷工一定要有足夠人數去發揮罷工嘅威力同保護性。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️短期目標⚠️<br />\n各行各業打工仔set 咗個短期目標<br />\n15/11前：三罷頻道要過5萬subscribe<br />\n22/11前：新四大工會過5000個會員申請<br />\n29/11前：第二批新工會成立<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2）文宣文宣文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論係搞真罷工、定叫人入會，都需要大量文宣<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得點解我地6月7月人數連綿不絕？就係因為各區街站同放映不斷開花！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstrikebooth\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstrikebooth&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=acb61669\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstrikebooth</a><br />\n<br />\n打工仔要撐罷工，唔係打工既更加要撐！<br />\n<br />\n因為罷工一定會面對好多壓力，為罷工手足提供輿論支持好重要，罷工手足面對的經濟同心理壓力就少啲孤單嘅感覺！<br />\n<br />\n最重要係！有民意基礎，令老闆有壓力，「容許」員工罷工！<br />\n<br />\n預左比人屌分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338512e6897f47b24db844f2126c81743d2f3d92","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"4c373ed386710f5498dbe5f3a2c8b28c11a40f96","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"caf471fca4ae90094dcae6ab7d1a47efbb8c2073","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"603fcb5c7576928c35101edff32f250be8c65018","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"c2ad26413d740abab0dda200f27a44e22ced7add","tid":1707212,"uid":331879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"幾時先真三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ac65c035dd99e6d02b490423a534810c292929","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"8ab75ad0464c8f0d5bc24ca08e47a21eeab179bf","tid":1707212,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"推到搞到有組織既罷工"},{"pid":"a792b459cbeb7f08ad14ea390524ad33175705a8","tid":1707212,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e85169